17:32.219 --> 17:35.389
For reminding me
of why I got into law in the first place:

17:35.389 --> 17:37.808
to fight for the little guy.

17:37.808 --> 17:40.394
Which is why
I said <i>"Hasta Lucia"</i> to my firm,

17:40.394 --> 17:42.354
and took a job
at your firm, brobeans.

17:42.354 --> 17:44.481
Don't "brobeans" me.

17:44.565 --> 17:47.651
My boss would never hire you
after the way you lied to us.

17:47.651 --> 17:50.028
I told him I'd take every
last bit of manipulation,

17:50.112 --> 17:52.406
deception, and accidental
pen-dropping

17:52.406 --> 17:56.368
I used against you guys and
put it towards saving the world.

17:56.368 --> 17:57.452
Even if that's true,

17:57.536 --> 18:00.914
I'm still not sure
that I can forgive you.

18:00.998 --> 18:03.375
Would you object to
an 11:15 brunch rezzy for two

18:03.375 --> 18:05.502
tomorrow at the Popover Pantry?

18:08.714 --> 18:12.217
- I'll allow it.
- Yes! The Brunch Bros are back!

18:14.386 --> 18:17.222
And thank God we were, because...

18:17.306 --> 18:21.143
well, what he said next is the reason
that I'm sitting in this chair.

18:21.143 --> 18:25.189
Seriously, thanks
for giving my soul a little redempsh.

18:25.189 --> 18:28.483
And B-T-dubs,
that judge was an idiot.

18:28.567 --> 18:30.444
It's people like you,

18:30.444 --> 18:33.614
people with hope
and vision and integ,

18:33.614 --> 18:36.450
