making the calls.

18:37.910 --> 18:40.913
And that's when I realized
I wanted to be a judge.

18:40.913 --> 18:43.957
Because judges are the ones
who can effect real change.

18:44.041 --> 18:45.792
And that's why I'm here,

18:45.876 --> 18:48.837
before the New York State
Judiciary Committee.

18:48.921 --> 18:51.548
I hope that you will consider me

18:51.632 --> 18:54.343
for an appointment
to a judgeship.

18:54.343 --> 18:55.761
Thank you, Mr. Eriksen.

18:55.761 --> 18:58.722
The panel will take this
under advisement.

18:58.722 --> 19:00.766
Take your time.

19:02.476 --> 19:04.311
It could be a few months.

19:06.647 --> 19:08.023
Better tell my wife
I won't be home for dinner.

19:08.023 --> 19:09.358
Get out.

19:14.530 --> 19:15.614
Hey.

19:15.614 --> 19:16.782
- Hey!
- How are you?

19:16.782 --> 19:20.786
- Uh, great. You?
- So gr...

19:20.786 --> 19:22.496
Can we talk about this
for a second?

19:22.496 --> 19:24.748
Yeah.

19:24.748 --> 19:27.918
It is super-weird between us,
and I don't want it to be.

19:27.918 --> 19:29.127
Me, neither.

19:29.211 --> 19:31.547
So let me just say this.

19:31.547 --> 19:33.131
I'm done.

19:33.215 --> 19:35.926
You don't have
to worry anymore.

19:35.926 --> 19:39.012
- What do you mean?
- I'm done trying to get you.

19:39.096 --> 19:40.764
I can't do it anymore.

19:40.848 --> 19:42.474
I'm sorry it's taken me
this long to figure it out,

19:42.558 --> 19:45.602
but I promise...

19:45.686 --> 19:48.146
I'm done making
a fool of myself.

19:48.230 --> 19:50.065
Barney, you haven't been making
a fool out of yourself...

19:50.065 --> 19:51.984
It's okay. It's okay.

19:51.984 --> 19:54.778
I want it to be okay.

19:54.862 --> 19:56.363
So here's what's
gonna happen.

19:56.363 --> 19:58.740
I'm gonna get us two drinks,

19:58.824 --> 20:01.577
come back and comment
on the likely size and color

20:01.577 --> 20:03.787
of the nipples
on that redhead at the bar,

20:03.871 --> 20:06.123
with the big, dark nipples.

20:06.123 --> 20:07.624
And you're gonna
be grossed out,

20:07.708 --> 20:09.918
