"that bitch Patrice" at work,

20:13.172 --> 20:15.048
but neither one of us
are gonna say,

20:15.132 --> 20:17.259
"Hey, how's it going?"
or "Good to see you!"

20:17.259 --> 20:20.179
Because it really will be
good to see you.

20:22.347 --> 20:24.016
Think we can swing that?

20:25.309 --> 20:26.476
Yeah, I do.

20:28.353 --> 20:30.314
Badass.

20:41.658 --> 20:42.951
Huh.

20:47.664 --> 20:50.334
Thanks for your support, guys.
It means a lot.

20:52.127 --> 20:54.379
We'll call in sick anytime
you have a problem.

20:58.842 --> 21:01.303
Lily coming!

21:04.097 --> 21:05.641
Badass.
